name: YujieMix
description:
6.4

昨天没事干又想办法把藤原和鱼介的上色结合了起来,效果感觉还不错,就把这个模型放到D位置吧。顺便把C的预览图重新跑了一下

I had nothing to do yesterday, so I combined the color styles of fuzichoco and Ononoimyoko models, and the result was not bad. I'll place this model in position D. Also, I ran the preview images of version C again

===========================================================

6.2

拿着鱼介和类似的模型到处乱融,融出了几个还不错的模型,以下是简单版本介绍以及注意事项

Taking Ononoimyoko and similar models everywhere to mix together, some good models were produced. Here is a brief introduction and some notes to keep in mind.

A是在鱼介上色基础上再加了一些乱七八糟的上色

B是鱼介和画师Torino结合

C是我把鱼介颜色给弄掉了,得加载VAE使用，请使用我提供的VAE

"A" added some random coloring on top of the coloring based on Ononoimyoko models.

"B" is a combination of Ononoimyoko models and Torino.

"C" is when I removed the coloring of the Ononoimyoko models, and had to load VAE.Please using the VAE I provided

注意A与B可以不加载额外的VAE就能很好的运作，C版的预览图都是未加载VAE的效果,具体效果看图吧

Note that both A and B can operate well without the need for additional VAE loading. Please be aware that the preview images for the C version are without VAE loaded. Please refer to the images for specific results
